reviewText:
Pros:

- Literally a throwback into PS1 THPS;
- Good graphics;
- Good soundtrack;
- Enchanced gameplay;

Cons:

- Bugs are common (physics mainly);
- If you want a game like the THPS PS2 series, that's not your game;
- Not the best experience without a controller.

Rating: 85/100 - Worth it!

